Package com.st.st25sdk.type5

Provides classes to handle NFC Forum Type5 Family Tags and Dynamic Tags.

See: Description

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    STType5PasswordInterface
    Defines the method to be implemented to handle a STMicroelectronics Type5 Tag supporting passwords
    STVicinityConfigInterface
    Defines common methods to be implemented to handle STMicroelectronics Vicinity tag configuration
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    CCFile
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Capability Container file
    CCFileType5
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Type5 Capability Container file
    CCFileVicinity
    Defines methods to handle a Vicinity Capability Container file
    ReadBlockResult
    Class containing the response of Iso15693 readBlocks() used for Type5 and Vicinity commands.
    STAreaContent
    Defines methods to handle STMicroelectronics Type5 Areas
    STType5MultiAreaTag
    Defines methods to handle a STMicroelectronics Type5 multi-area tag
    STType5Sector
    Defines methods to handle a STMicroelectronics Type5 sector tag
    STType5Tag
    Defines methods to handle STMicroelectronics Type5 Tag
    STVicinityTag
    Defines methods to handle a STMicroelectronics Vicinity Tag
    SysFile
    Defines methods to handle a System file
    SysFileType5
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Type5 System file
    SysFileType5Extended
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum type5 extended System file
    SysFileVicinity
    Defines methods to handle a Vicinity System file
    Type5Tag
    Defines methods to handle a NFC Forum Type5 Tag
